text: Hossam Mohamed Ashour Sanad Atia (, born 9 March 1986) is an Egyptian former footballer who played as a defensive midfielder. == Honours == * Egyptian Premier League: 2004–05, 2005–06, 2006–07, 2007–08, 2008–09, 2009–10, 2010–11, 2013–14, 2015–16, 2016–17, 2017–18 * Egypt Cup: 2005–06, 2006–07, 2016–17 * Egyptian Super Cup: 2005, 2006, 2007, 2008, 2010, 2011, 2014, 2015, 2017 * CAF Champions League: 2005, 2006, 2008, 2012, 2013 * CAF Confederation Cup: 2014 * African Super Cup: 2006, 2007, 2009, 2013, 2014 == References == == Other websites == * * * Category:1986 births Category:Egyptian footballers Category:Living people Category:Egypt international footballers
title: Hossam Ashour
